What is differnce b/w query parameter nad path parameter 

✅ Path Parameters → When you need to uniquely identify a resource (e.g., user ID, order ID).
✅ Query Parameters → When you need to filter, search, or modify the request (e.g., sorting, pagination, filtering)

URL Sent: https://api.example.com/users/123
Given url "https://api.example.com"
And path "users", "123"
When method GET
Then status 200


https://api.example.com/users?role=admin&status=active
Given url "https://api.example.com/users"
And param role = "admin"
And param status = "active"
When method GET
Then status 200


